  <refnamediv>
    <refname>whitening</refname>

    <refpurpose>Whitening transformation.</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>

  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <title>Calling Sequence</title>

    <synopsis>[new_mat, Aw] = whitening(mat)</synopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>

  <refsection>
    <title>Parameters</title>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>mat</term>

        <listitem>
          <para>Input matrix.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term>new_mat</term>

        <listitem>
          <para>New matrix after whitening transformation.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term>Aw</term>

        <listitem>
          <para>Whitening matrix.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </refsection>

  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>

    <para>The function <emphasis>whitening</emphasis> converts the covariance
    matrix of the input <emphasis>mat</emphasis> into the identity
    matrix.</para>
  </refsection>

